FIG. 2 is a schematic of an embodiment of the monitoring system of FIG. 1 configured to monitor turbomachine blades, in accordance with an aspect of the present disclosure;
FIG. 3 is an expanded view of an embodiment of a composite material forming the turbine casing of FIG. 2, in accordance with an aspect of the present disclosure;
FIG. 4 is an expanded view of an embodiment of a composite material forming the turbomachine blades of FIG. 2, in accordance with an aspect of the present disclosure;
FIG. 5 is a schematic of an embodiment of a display of FIG. 2 displaying emission spectra generated by the monitoring system of FIG. 2, in accordance with an aspect of the present disclosure; and
FIG. 6 is a process flow diagram illustrating an embodiment of a method for monitoring mechanoluminescent emissions from a turbomachine and controlling an operational parameter based on the monitored emissions, in accordance with an aspect of the present disclosure.
